{"tid":763753,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】美擬將1.56萬億中國貨關稅增至25% 中國外交部：必定反制","createTime":"2018-08-01T11:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T14:59:16.000Z","uid":174649,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f544fb812bef3affece3f027e2056f9b35cc5e54","tid":763753,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180801/small/1533092976_e851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180801%2Fsmall%2F1533092976_e851.jpg&h=dd07d34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外電報道指，美國總統特朗普將會提交對中國進口貨品總值2,000億美元的關稅，由原定的10%加至25%，以此向北京施壓。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部回應，指如果美方採取進一步升級舉動，中方必然會予以反制，在中美經貿問題的立場是非常堅定、明確的，沒有改變。美方的施壓和訛詐不會起作用。然而，中方始終主張通過對話協商處理中美之間的貿易摩擦，對話必須建立在相互尊重和平等的基礎上，建立在規則之上，建立在信用之上，單方面威脅和施壓只會適得其反。<br />\n特朗普早前曾表示，會額外對中國總值2,000億美元的進口貨收10%關稅，但有傳未來幾日，美國會公布將關稅由10%加至25%。特朗普已指示美國貿易代表萊蒂澤（Robert Lighthizer）進行此計劃。<br />\n美國貿易代表辦公室將於8月20至23日召開聽證會，審議中國總值2,000億美元的進口貨關稅政策，公眾諮詢期將於8月30日結束。<br />\n此前，消息人士指美國財長姆欽和中國國務院副總理劉鶴的代表，正在進行私下對話，尋找重新啟動談判的方式，並指具體的時間表、待討論的事項以及談判的形式尚未最終確定，但補充說已就雙方需要進行更多磋商達成共識，因為雙方的磋商仍處於非常初級的階段，彼此都認為對方應該先做表示，故現時的貿易談判進展不大。<br />\n此外，下一輪美國關稅最快將於周三生效，可能會對另外160億美元中國輸美商品加徵關稅。"},{"pid":"2728882093dcca03c0afa9a2094f3a6055bdceaf","tid":763753,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180801/large/1533092976_e851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180801%2Flarge%2F1533092976_e851.jpg&h=7ef66e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1729648c35190d98d8877d7c5ebd729e2a5866c0","tid":763753,"uid":180404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:12:53.000Z","msg":"又跌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3543b52382f335e0017a08cca436a25d4f39a506","tid":763753,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650dfb2930f96cc2b416aa9222d79708c00aeec4","tid":763753,"uid":166785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:56:43.000Z","msg":"仲串77"},{"pid":"01e38f5167de758209e2808ff2220078db38b0f5","tid":763753,"uid":180156,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"強國唔夠打就投降喇<br />\n搞衰晒個股市"},{"pid":"eb86d3b84edc992c435d049bf957f0bd1e524850","tid":763753,"uid":170601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"到2025年，你便知死！"},{"pid":"71b1ac8522ca7d74f386249245bdfe5565aabcc1","tid":763753,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e38f5167de758209e2808ff2220078db38b0f5","tid":763753,"uid":180156,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"強國唔夠打就投降喇<br />\n搞衰晒個股市"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"呢句真，搞跌個市帶黎負財富效應你真係衰多兩錢"},{"pid":"332ec103afe3555f982e8be9db753b325f836d27","tid":763753,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"277牛死定了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5089abc986466162dec9194ac9fa5a6aff623ffd","tid":763753,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"650dfb2930f96cc2b416aa9222d79708c00aeec4","tid":763753,"uid":166785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:56:43.000Z","msg":"仲串77"},"cit